title: Hello Kitty and Sanrio Machine Embroidery Designs and ebooks
description:
Selection of Hello Kitty and Sanrio machine embroidery files in PES format.  You can easily convert them to work with your machine using free software like Bernina ARTlink/Wilcom or similar.

Includes official Brother card designs of Hello kitty, Pochacco, Marron Cream, Keroppi, Badtz Maru as well as some handmade designs.  There are 2 designs of Rebecca BonBon and 1 design of Rirakkuma.

Also included is a hand embroidery and cross stitch book in Japanese for Sanrio characters and a book for crochet with the characters.

Please help seed for others.
